reviews.review_text:
Morning Dew! I can't believe there are no reviews yet of this recording. There are about a dozen sources for this show, and this one is far and away the best. This is one of the best audience recordings I've ever heard. If every AUD was like this, I'd never need another SBD. 

This is a really hot show all the way through, but the real standout is the Morning Dew. This is how the song was meant to be played.
